<br>
&quot;Hello sisters!  As many may already know, I have spent much time and a great deal of platinum coins upon my jewelry.  I taken a test from my dear Amber just this day, and scored a 220, my highest ever!<br>
<br>
I set up my wares this day because I have recently begun work upon rings fashioned of Jasper gems and platinum bars.  I have already created well over 80 such rings, and will see many more.  I know many of my brothers and sisters will find such rings quite useful, so I wish to make them available.<br>
<br>
Such being said, I shall create these rings for any brother, sister, or close friend of in return for the platinum needed to purchase materials.  I apoligize for having to do such for all, but I would find myself out of platinum and unable to continue my crafting due to lack of coins if I do not.  Rings of jasper gems and bars of platinum currently cost myself 106 platinum coins.<br>
<br>
I do also wish to make known that I will create any and all forms of jewelry that you so desire for the same costs to yourself.  If you desire jewelry of gold, or electrum, I shall create yourself such.  <br>
<br>
If you are in need of jewelry created from Velium, I shall create yourself such... although you may wish to know I have not yet perfected my work with such metals, and do tend to fail at my attempts two times for every ten attempts, even with my borrowed gnomish device (*hugs Rorack*).  For work with such metals, I will ask that you provide myself with the coins for the materials, and accept the risk of their loss to yourself should my hands slip.  Again, I apoligize for such, but I do fear I would quickly lose all I hold within my pockets do I not.  =( &quot;<br>
<br>
*You see that the note is signed in a flourish of beautiful letters, that, after studing for a moment, can be read as 'Ayrielle'* <br>
